"title": "8786: opposition, to sin and evil",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8786: opposition, to sin and evil",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Believers are called upon to opppose all that is hostile to God's purposes in the world.</p>\n<h2>God opposes evil</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:12-Matt21:13\">MAT 21:12–21:13</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:15-Mark11:16\">MRK 11:15–11:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:45-Luke19:46\">LUK 19:45–19:46</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:14-John2:17\">JHN 2:14–2:17</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod4:24\">EXO 4:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:3\">LEV 20:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:14-Lev26:17\">LEV 26:14–26:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num22:22\">NUM 22:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:2-Mal3:5\">MAL 3:2–3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:6\">JAS 4:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:5\">1PE 5:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:16\">REV 2:16</a></p>\n<h2>God's people should oppose evil</h2>\n<h3>Within themselves</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:5\">COL 3:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:29-Matt5:30\">MAT 5:29–5:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:13\">ROM 8:13</a></p>\n<h3>Among themselves</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:11\">GAL 2:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor5:12-1Cor5:13\">1CO 5:12–5:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:3\">EPH 5:3</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of failure to oppose evil</h2>\n<h3>Within the church</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor5:1-1Cor5:2\">1CO 5:1–5:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:20\">REV 2:20</a></p>\n<h3>Within the family</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam3:13\">1SA 3:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs1:6\">1KI 1:6</a></p>\n<h3>Within the state</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:4\">HAB 1:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg5:23\">JDG 5:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam15:9-1Sam15:11\">1SA 15:9–15:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:28\">JER 5:28</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of unwise opposition to evil</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:51-Matt26:52\">MAT 26:51–26:52</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:47\">MRK 14:47</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:50-Luke22:51\">LUK 22:50–22:51</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:10-John18:11\">JHN 18:10–18:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:54-Luke9:55\">LUK 9:54–9:55</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:13-Acts19:16\">ACT 19:13–19:16</a></p>\n<h2>Opposing evil by doing good</h2>\n<h3>Commanded by God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:15\">1PE 2:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:44\">MAT 5:44</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:20-Rom12:21\">ROM 12:20–12:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:15\">1TH 5:15</a></p>\n<h3>Exemplified in Scripture</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num12:13\">NUM 12:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam24:17\">1SA 24:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam26:11\">1SA 26:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:22\">2KI 6:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:51\">LUK 22:51</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:34\">LUK 23:34</a></p>\n<h2>Motives for opposing evil</h2>\n<h3>Concern for the honour and glory of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num25:6-Num25:13\">NUM 25:6–25:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:10\">1KI 19:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek28:22\">EZK 28:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:17\">JHN 2:17</a></p>\n<h3>Concern for the good of others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:4-Gal2:5\">GAL 2:4–2:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut17:12-Deut17:13\">DEU 17:12–17:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:20\">1TI 5:20</a></p>",
